\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 Illustration of binge watching a tv show for hours and then that is all you can think about when you go to bed\'85it is what you put into your mind that comes out of your mind.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
