\fs36 \cf0 GOD
\fs24 \uc0\u8232 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f1 \cf3 3\'a0
\f2\b0 Since, then, you have been raised with Christ,\'a0set your hearts on things above, \
\
where Christ is, seated at the right hand of God.\'a0 
\f1\b \super 2\'a0
\f2\b0 \nosupersub Set your minds on things above, not on earthly things.\'a0\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Question \'96 Where is your mind and what is set on?\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\f3\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}In the past few weeks we a culture seem to be focused on some other things right?\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If you have been raised in Christ is there a seriousness about pursuing God?
\f3\b0 \cf0   And what does that look like?  So HOW?  How do you go about having your mind transformed and becoming more and more like Jesus?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf3 \super 3\'a0
\f2\b0 \nosupersub For you died,\'a0\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So much of our lives even after becoming a Christian is centered around us living for ourselves\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We tend to talk about our personal preferences and what we want in life and who we are\'85YOU\'92RE DEAD!\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3 and your life is now hidden with Christ in God.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\'a0
\f1\b \super 4\'a0
\f2\b0 \nosupersub When Christ, who is your life,\'a0appears,\'a0then you also will appear with him in glory.\
\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\f1\b \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Would someone else know that Christ is your life?\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl1
\f2\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is different than someone knowing you\'92re a Christian.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 \super 5\'a0
\f3\b0 \nosupersub Put to death,\'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The imagery here is to fight in battle \'96 not to coddle it or play with it.  It is fire and will consume you!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You can fight or drift\'85it is your call\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}For all of us we have to decide what we want to fight.  \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Do we fight against sin or Jesus?
\f3\b0 \cf0   \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I can still be a Christian and do this\'85\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s not that big of a deal!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Is God dragging you kicking and screaming into His holiness or are you following excitingly?  \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We are raised with Him meaning we are tied to Him.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3 therefore, whatever belongs to your earthly nature:\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Part of this mean to search our hearts and minds and categorize what belongs where\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}All of us have things in our lives that belong in certain categories.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}As long as we don\'92t know where they belong there is a temptation to be able to ignore it \'96 I didn\'92t think about it really?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf4 The bulk of what hinders your relationship with God isn\'92t morally bad but probably morally neutral.\
\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f3\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There is no verse against\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}TV, Hobbies, Internet or Facebook, weight loss, a baby, video games, and Movies aren\'92t evil\'85we are!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What we do is pursue these things instead of God\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3 sexual immorality, impurity, lust, evil desires and greed,\'a0which is idolatry.\'a0
\f0\b \super 6\'a0
\f3\b0 \nosupersub Because of these, the wrath of God\'a0is coming. \
\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I think it is really important here to pause and just point out something.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God becomes angry and while He is love that doesn\'92t mean that is all He is.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There is this belief that because God is love He can\'92t be anything else that is uncomfortable.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So when someone talks about God\'92s  love or wrath people get all bent out of shape and start talking about how loving God is\'85as if it is some trump card on everything.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God is loving\'85but with loves comes many other things in life\'85in fact because He is loving He has to do other things.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 \super  7\'a0
\f3\b0 \nosupersub You used to walk in these ways, in the life you once lived.\'a0\
\
\

\f0\b \super 8\'a0
\f3\b0 \nosupersub But now you must also rid yourselves\'a0of all such things as these: anger, rage, malice, slander,\'a0and filthy language from your lips.\
\
\'a0
\f0\b \super 9\'a0
\f3\b0 \nosupersub Do not lie to each other,\'a0since you have taken off your old self\'a0with its practices\'a0\
\

\f0\b \super 10\'a0
\f3\b0 \nosupersub and have put on the new self,\'a0which is being renewed\'a0in knowledge in the image of its Creator.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I hear from people \'96 that just isn\'92t me\'85well good\'85because it isn\'92t about you anymore!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Things must be renewed because they get stale and old and irrelevant.  Verse 10 sounds very close to Romans 12:2\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 CONCLUSION:\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f3\b0\fs24 \cf0 Does your current lifestyle fit your new self?  If it does and it is not Godly you should question which self you have on you.\
\
	\
 If you have been raised in Christ is there a seriousness about pursuing God?  \
\
\
